{"tid":676381,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"巴絲有冇比找換店呃過錢？","createTime":"2018-05-24T10:16:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-24T14:50:09.000Z","uid":128151,"like":0,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"08f47465270e6c2c7409170f3caaf35dd6eec4f5","tid":676381,"uid":128151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T10:16:35.000Z","msg":"是咁的，岩岩去左間中環好出名既找換店<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 換外幣，盛惠港紙三萬鬆 。<br />\n<br />\n咁我拎左一疊一早數好既五百蚊紙比佢數，望住佢用手數左次就話仲差一千蚊。我果下不疑有詐，話哂人地都開左咁多年，就拎左出黎叫佢數多次。<br />\n<br />\n點知，佢好似撞聾聽唔到咁，淨係叫我去後面等等。我望一望隔離啤鳩住我既蝻亞實Q，再望一望後面成隊唔耐煩既香港人，我淆左，惟有死死氣行左去後面等拎錢。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n樓主係on9架喇但麻煩高抬貴手，屌得細力啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有冇巴絲遇過類似既事？"},{"pid":"f99f8502e0bad6e6ac70c6d9788d87fab9fdafc3","tid":676381,"uid":62822,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T10:28:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1a90c3890d95a27c4eaf5651a44076638bb6c6df","tid":676381,"uid":58503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T10:29:08.000Z","msg":"好多年前係佐敦比人呃過一次，個手法一樣係人手數完話少左1張。"},{"pid":"6f5fbf78735b62ad5af4155b37318f396d703cc1","tid":676381,"uid":43530,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T10:37:34.000Z","msg":"正路手數完要過多次機<br />\n你可以叫佢過機你睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed5a64dc2e5b9dae3192412c4b3f2677e59e1f3e","tid":676381,"uid":99205,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T12:26:57.000Z","msg":"爆名吧"},{"pid":"fcf4e98996c4559853a57ae3cd8dd2c377d146c2","tid":676381,"uid":128151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f99f8502e0bad6e6ac70c6d9788d87fab9fdafc3","tid":676381,"uid":62822,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T10:28:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T13:02:43.000Z","msg":"岩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後報左驚都話幫我唔到"},{"pid":"a0b3097703dbcb421f016c3822778fbdda38f854","tid":676381,"uid":128151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6f5fbf78735b62ad5af4155b37318f396d703cc1","tid":676381,"uid":43530,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T10:37:34.000Z","msg":"正路手數完要過多次機<br />\n你可以叫佢過機你睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T13:03:25.000Z","msg":"我果陣都奇怪 咁大間行做幾廿年都人手數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4307b708822937f7291d9c326101bf1db8d33168","tid":676381,"uid":128151,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"ed5a64dc2e5b9dae3192412c4b3f2677e59e1f3e","tid":676381,"uid":99205,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T12:26:57.000Z","msg":"爆名吧"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T13:07:30.000Z","msg":"出名排長龍"},{"pid":"9c84026ca1990e215d9e904c19242050954448ab","tid":676381,"uid":33336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T13:08:53.000Z","msg":"係咪99+1 年？<br />\n<br />\n我去開呢間都無事喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf1ef21511407248edd22a3155becee799345ad2","tid":676381,"uid":5058,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T13:08:55.000Z","msg":"百年？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54cdcc92f3ea7738bfb8ccc2436a298484f19ad5","tid":676381,"uid":20933,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T13:10:11.000Z","msg":"100年出曬名"},{"pid":"972f79b7c22b55837696d6196ae9ad89440416c7","tid":676381,"uid":128151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9c84026ca1990e215d9e904c19242050954448ab","tid":676381,"uid":33336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T13:08:53.000Z","msg":"係咪99+1 年？<br />\n<br />\n我去開呢間都無事喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad